26 to 28. Lalipul border will also remain open only from 10 am to 11 am in the morning and 4 pm to 5 pm in the evening.","title":"Three border points in Darchula opened for few days - Khabarhub","url":"http://english.khabarhub.com/2020/27/144766/","video":[]}
